cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper is about teaching robots to imitate humans and perform tasks. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of meta-learning and control policies. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is mentioned in the paper as a way to extract features from images. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper discusses the use of machine learning to teach robots. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also relevant as the paper discusses control policies and sim-to-real transfer.
